    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mushrooman 是一款大氣的第一人稱生存恐怖遊戲。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2>深夜，你在茂密的森林中沿著高速公路行駛，璀璨的星光照亮了你的道路，參天大樹在風中搖曳，一切都很好……然而，你的車突然沒油了。試著找一個加油站，但要小心，你並不孤單。一些可怕的東西（例如巨大的毒菌）在這些森林中漫遊。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187570/extras/06be60a5d2416452d97808b36eaa3174.poster.avif?t=1751572750\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187570/extras/06be60a5d2416452d97808b36eaa3174.webm?t=1751572750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187570/extras/06be60a5d2416452d97808b36eaa3174.mp4?t=1751572750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器和物品</h2>使用你能找到的所有有用的物品。為了生存，您需要探索該位置。使用食物和水、藥丸和急救箱來治癒傷口並恢復體力。燈籠或蠟燭可以幫助您在這片黑暗的森林中不迷路，而手槍可以讓您擊退侵略性的怪物，或者至少不會感到那麼無助。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187570/extras/23b1389e674a68487dc20edbf7728508.poster.avif?t=1751572750\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187570/extras/23b1389e674a68487dc20edbf7728508.webm?t=1751572750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187570/extras/23b1389e674a68487dc20edbf7728508.mp4?t=1751572750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地點</h2>在該類型的最佳傳統中，這是一片森林。茂密的黑暗森林。盡量記住該地區並按照地圖進行操作，以免迷路並打擾當地人。雖然，我在說什麼，他們無論如何都會注意到你。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187570/extras/ffb684df585926f9cb741e90d888c508.poster.avif?t=1751572750\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187570/extras/ffb684df585926f9cb741e90d888c508.webm?t=1751572750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遊戲特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 經典的獨立恐怖氛圍。你一個人在這裡，幫助不會來，一個昏暗的手電筒（也經常耗盡電池）是你唯一的朋友。<br></li><li> 如果你想離開這裡，你需要探索的大氣夜森林。<br></li><li> 尋找武器和其他有用的物品。這將幫助你生存。<br></li><li> 設置、管理和保存進度的詳細菜單。<br></li><li> 蘑菇是殺手。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187570/extras/53e0faa36603fac301d2ccd3694a0afb.poster.avif?t=1751572750\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187570/extras/53e0faa36603fac301d2ccd3694a0afb.webm?t=1751572750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187570/extras/53e0faa36603fac301d2ccd3694a0afb.mp4?t=1751572750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
